      "description": "settings(ParseSettings) updates parser settings and settings() returns the new object",
      "path": "B0→B1→B2",
      "precondition": "Parser created via htmlParser()",
      "expectedResult": "settings() == the passed ParseSettings instance",
      "tags": [
        "positive",
